oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Pitner's Map of Knoxville 1930

oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Pitner's Map of Knoxville, Tennessee. Published by Carl Pitner 945 Pennsylvania Ave., N.W. Washington, D.C. Copyright by Carl Pitner. 1930. Includes Oakwood, Park City, South Knoxville, Mechanicsville, West Knoxville, Sequoyah Hills, Lonsdale, Vestal, East Knoxville, North Knoxville, Lincoln Park, Fountain City, and City Wards.
